text: Árpád Csonka (born 24 August 1991) is a Slovak football striker of Hungarian ethnicity who currently plays for the Corgoň Liga club FK DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda. ==External links== * at fcdac1904.com ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:Slovak footballers Category:FC DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Hungarians in Slovakia
